{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/wordo_normal.png?t=1729282094\" />Hi there! <strong>Wordban</strong>'s free demo is ready! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wordban</strong> is a text-based Sokoban-style game where you control the adorable <strong>Wordo</strong> to push boxes and trigger each level's innovative text rules, changing the layout, quantity, and even the attributes of the boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/description_gameplay.gif?t=1729282094\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/wordo_ei.png?t=1729282094\" />With your strategy, <strong>Wordo</strong> can make boxes multiply, merge into one, drip through stone, or even turn into gold! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the <strong>Wordban Demo</strong>, you can enjoy a free preview of the game's 1st chapter: <strong>The Room</strong>, featuring 20 unique levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/description_chapter1.gif?t=1729282094\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/wordo_uwu.png?t=1729282094\" />Awaken <strong>Wordo</strong> and enjoy the special puzzle-solving fun!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wake Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima